cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.CR 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on analyzing the performance of neural networks on a comprehension task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses statistical cues and adversarial datasets, which could fall under cs.CC (Computational Complexity) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
